| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7514 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 112bc5a4-4637-553a-95de-39aabbb0f45e"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
